00:23:18.900 --> 00:23:21.240
is a Google product,
we definitely

00:23:21.240 --> 00:23:24.330
wanted to stay
true to that voice.

00:23:24.330 --> 00:23:27.390
But there are many
Google products,

00:23:27.390 --> 00:23:29.670
