00:23:42.510 --> 00:23:44.490
because mobile
payment apps are still

00:23:44.490 --> 00:23:49.270
seen as a thing of the future,
especially here in the US.

00:23:49.270 --> 00:23:52.830
And research showed that
we had an opportunity

00:23:52.830 --> 00:23:56.070
to appeal to the more emotional
dimensions of the Android Pay

00:23:56.070 --> 00:23:58.800
experience like the
