So we've heard from Allison
about the best practices in UX

00:37:01.620 --> 00:37:04.220
writing, heard about
brand voice just now,

00:37:04.220 --> 00:37:07.730
and I wanted to reflect
on our first sad screen.

00:37:07.730 --> 00:37:10.260
I think we can do better, right?

00:37:10.260 --> 00:37:12.200
All right, let's
