00:37:12.200 --> 00:37:14.960
and do a quick on-brand edit.

00:37:14.960 --> 00:37:18.530
So a simple way to make this
much more positive and much

00:37:18.530 --> 00:37:21.560
more useful is, "Ready
to add some friends?

00:37:21.560 --> 00:37:23.450
Import your contacts."

00:37:23.450 --> 00:37:26.570
So adding that simple call to
action, import your contacts,

00:37:26.570 --> 00:37:29.510
could help the user get started
and, ultimately, have a better

00:37:29.510 --> 00:37:32.570
relationship with this app.

